headline: The Home Depot Declares First-Quarter Dividend of $2.30
summary: The Home Depot®, the world's largest home improvement retailer, today announced that its board of directors declared a first-quarter cash dividend of $2.30 per share. The dividend is payable on June 18, 2025, to shareholders of record at the close of business on June 5, 2025. This is the 153rd consecutive quarter the company has paid a cash dividend.
